---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Breadcrumbs from '../../../components/Breadcrumbs.astro';
import CTAButton from '../../../components/CTAButton.astro';
import { COMPANY_INFO } from '../../../utils/constants';

const lang = 'en';
const post = {
  title: 'Isuzu GIGA Prime Mover EXZ Malaysia: Financing & Specs Guide 2026',
  slug: 'giga-prime-exz-malaysia-financing-guide',
  excerpt: 'Complete guide to financing the Isuzu GIGA Prime Mover EXZ in Malaysia. 460 bhp, AMT transmission, 60-ton capacity. Get 0% down payment options with flexible terms.',
  date: '2026-03-13',
  author: 'Ing Heng Credit Team',
  readTime: 8,
  category: 'Transport Vehicles',
  image: '/images/blog/prime-mover-financing.jpg'
};

const keywords = ['giga prime exz malaysia', 'isuzu giga prime mover', 'prime mover financing', 'giga exz price malaysia', 'isuzu prime mover 460 bhp'],
  breadcrumbItems = [
  { label: 'Home', href: '/en' },
  { label: 'Blog', href: '/en/blog' },
  { label: post.title, href: `/en/blog/${post.slug}` }
];
---

<BaseLayout title={post.title} description={post.excerpt} lang={lang} keywords={keywords}>
  <script type="application/ld+json">
    {
      "@context": "https://schema.org",
      "@type": "BlogPosting",
      "headline": post.title,
      "description": post.excerpt,
      "datePublished": post.date,
      "author": { "@type": "Organization", "name": post.author },
      "publisher": {
        "@type": "Organization",
        "name": "Ing Heng Credit & Leasing Sdn Bhd",
        "logo": {
          "@type": "ImageObject",
          "url": "https://inghengcredit.com/logo.png"
        }
      }
    }
  </script>

  <Breadcrumbs items={breadcrumbItems} />

  <article class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <header class="mb-8">
      <span class="text-sm font-semibold" style="color: #D4A574;">Transport Vehicles</span>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mt-2" style="color: #2D1810; font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase;">{post.title}</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mt-4">{post.excerpt}</p>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4 text-sm text-gray-500 mt-4">
        <span>{post.author}</span>
        <span>•</span>
        <time>{new Date(post.date).toLocaleDateString('en-US', { year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric' })}</time>
        <span>•</span>
        <span>{post.readTime} min read</span>
      </div>
    </header>

    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
      <h2>The Isuzu GIGA Prime Mover EXZ: Heavy-Duty Power for Malaysian Haulers</h2>

      <p>Looking at the Isuzu GIGA Prime Mover EXZ for your fleet? You're eyeing one of the most capable prime movers in the Malaysian market. With 460 bhp and a 60-ton gross vehicle weight rating, this machine is built for serious haulage work. But here's the question most transport operators face: how do you finance a truck of this calibre without draining your working capital?</p>

      <p>At Ing Heng Credit, we've been financing heavy commercial vehicles for over 40 years. We understand that buying a prime mover isn't just about the specs—it's about keeping your cash flowing while your trucks are hauling.</p>

      <h2>GIGA Prime Mover EXZ: Full Specifications</h2>

      <p>Before we talk financing, let's look at what you're getting with the GIGA EXZ:</p>

      <h3>Engine & Performance</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Engine Displacement:</strong> 15,681 cc (15.7L diesel)</li>
        <li><strong>Maximum Power:</strong> 460 bhp @ 1,800 rpm</li>
        <li><strong>Maximum Torque:</strong> 2,256 Nm @ 900-1,300 rpm</li>
        <li><strong>Transmission:</strong> Automatic (AMT) - smooth shifting for long hauls</li>
        <li><strong>Fuel Tank:</strong> 400 litres - covers KL to Singapore and back</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>Dimensions & Capacity</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Gross Vehicle Weight:</strong> 60,000 kg (60 tons)</li>
        <li><strong>Overall Length:</strong> 7,800 mm</li>
        <li><strong>Overall Width:</strong> 2,300 mm</li>
        <li><strong>Overall Height:</strong> 1,800 mm</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>Safety & Handling</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Suspension:</strong> Semi-elliptical leaf springs (front & rear)</li>
        <li><strong>Brakes:</strong> Full air brake system</li>
      </ul>

      <p>This is a serious machine for serious work. Container haulage, heavy cargo, port operations—the GIGA EXZ handles it all.</p>

      <h2>Financing Options: How to Afford a GIGA Prime Mover</h2>

      <p>Let's be realistic. A prime mover at this level costs somewhere between RM350,000 to RM450,000 depending on configuration. Banks typically want 20-30% down payment. That's RM70,000 to RM135,000 cash upfront. Most transport companies would rather use that money for operations.</p>

      <h3>Ing Heng Credit: 0% Down Payment Available</h3>

      <p>Here's how our financing differs from traditional banks:</p>

      <table class="min-w-full border-collapse border border-gray-300 my-6">
        <thead>
          <tr class="bg-gray-100">
            <th class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2 text-left">Feature</th>
            <th class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2 text-left">Bank Financing</th>
            <th class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2 text-left">Ing Heng Credit</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2">Down Payment</td>
            <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2">20-30%</td>
            <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2"><strong>0% available</strong></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2">Approval Time</td>
            <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2">2-4 weeks</td>
            <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2"><strong>Fast processing</strong></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2">Age Restrictions</td>
            <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2">Strict age limits</td>
            <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2"><strong>No age limit</strong></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2">Credit History</td>
            <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2">Strict requirements</td>
            <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2"><strong>Case-by-case review</strong></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2">Industry Knowledge</td>
            <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2">Generalist lenders</td>
            <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2"><strong>40+ years in equipment</strong></td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>

      <h2>Monthly Payment Estimates for GIGA EXZ</h2>

      <p>Here's what your monthly obligations might look like with different financing terms:</p>

      <h3>Scenario: RM400,000 GIGA Prime Mover EXZ</h3>

      <p><strong>Bank Financing (20% Down):</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li>Down payment: RM80,000</li>
        <li>Loan amount: RM320,000</li>
        <li>5-year term: approximately RM6,500-RM7,500/month</li>
        <li>Cash tied up immediately: RM80,000</li>
      </ul>

      <p><strong>Ing Heng 0% Down Payment:</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li>Down payment: RM0</li>
        <li>Loan amount: RM400,000</li>
        <li>5-year term: approximately RM7,800-RM8,800/month</li>
        <li>Cash preserved: RM80,000 for operations</li>
      </ul>

      <p>Yes, the monthly payment is higher with 100% financing. But consider this: that RM80,000 you kept can cover diesel, driver wages, insurance, and road tax for months. Your truck starts earning from day one instead of draining your reserves.</p>

      <h2>Why the GIGA EXZ Suits Malaysian Operations</h2>

      <h3>Port Haulage Ready</h3>
      <p>Port Klang, Penang Port, Tanjung Pelepas—the GIGA EXZ's 60-ton GVW handles laden containers without breaking a sweat. The AMT transmission reduces driver fatigue during stop-start port traffic.</p>

      <h3>Long-Distance Capable</h3>
      <p>KL to Johor. KL to Penang. Singapore runs. The 400-litre fuel tank and 460 bhp engine mean fewer stops and more kilometres covered per day. Time is money in logistics.</p>

      <h3>Proven Reliability</h3>
      <p>Isuzu has been in Malaysia for decades. Parts availability is excellent. Workshop support nationwide. When your truck is your income, reliability matters more than anything else.</p>

      <h2>Documents You'll Need for Financing</h2>

      <p>Getting started with Ing Heng Credit is straightforward. Here's what we typically need:</p>

      <ul>
        <li>IC copy (owner/guarantor)</li>
        <li>Business registration (SSM)</li>
        <li>Bank statements (3-6 months)</li>
        <li>Quotation for the GIGA EXZ</li>
        <li>Existing fleet documents (if applicable)</li>
      </ul>

      <p>No need for perfect credit history. We review each application individually. Been rejected by a bank? Talk to us anyway—we've helped many transport operators who were turned away elsewhere.</p>

      <h2>Adding to Your Existing Fleet</h2>

      <p>Already running prime movers? We understand fleet expansion. Many operators add one truck at a time as business grows. Our financing considers your existing commitments and structures payments that your operations can support.</p>

      <p>Planning to buy multiple GIGA units? Fleet deals available. Contact us for volume pricing on financing.</p>

      <h2>Used vs New: Financing Both</h2>

      <p>Here's something banks won't tell you: we finance used prime movers too. Found a well-maintained GIGA EXZ with low mileage? We can structure financing for pre-owned units. Banks typically refuse vehicles over 5-10 years old. We're more flexible.</p>

      <p>Of course, new units often make sense for heavy usage. Lower maintenance, full warranty, latest technology. But if budget is the concern, used GIGA models with proper financing can get you earning sooner.</p>

      <h2>Operating Costs to Consider</h2>

      <p>Beyond the financing, budget for these monthly expenses:</p>

      <ul>
        <li><strong>Diesel:</strong> RM8,000-RM15,000/month depending on routes</li>
        <li><strong>Driver:</strong> RM3,000-RM4,500/month + allowances</li>
        <li><strong>Insurance:</strong> RM800-RM1,500/month</li>
        <li><strong>Maintenance:</strong> RM500-RM1,000/month reserve</li>
        <li><strong>Road Tax & Permits:</strong> Variable by route</li>
      </ul>

      <p>A well-utilized prime mover should generate RM25,000-RM40,000 in revenue monthly. The numbers work when you keep the truck moving.</p>

      <h2>GIGA EXZ vs Competitors</h2>

      <p>Comparing to other 60-ton class prime movers?</p>

      <ul>
        <li><strong>vs Hino:</strong> GIGA offers strong torque delivery and proven reliability. Both are excellent choices in Malaysia.</li>
        <li><strong>vs Fuso:</strong> Similar power class. GIGA's AMT is smoother according to many drivers. Parts availability comparable.</li>
        <li><strong>vs Volvo/Scania:</strong> European brands cost significantly more upfront and for parts. GIGA delivers 80% of the capability at 60% of the price.</li>
      </ul>

      <p>Whatever brand you choose, we can finance it. But the GIGA EXZ offers excellent value for Malaysian haulage operations.</p>

      <h2>Ready to Finance Your GIGA Prime Mover?</h2>

      <p>Don't let cash flow concerns stop you from growing your fleet. The Isuzu GIGA Prime Mover EXZ is a capable, proven workhorse for Malaysian logistics. With the right financing, you can add this machine to your fleet without draining your reserves.</p>

      <p>Get in touch for a free consultation. We'll review your situation, explain your options, and give you a clear picture of what financing looks like—no obligation, no pressure.</p>

      <CTAButton 
        text="Get a Free Quote" 
        href={`https://wa.me/${COMPANY_INFO.whatsapp.replace(/[^0-9]/g, '')}?text=Hi,%20I'm%20interested%20in%20financing%20for%20Isuzu%20GIGA%20Prime%20Mover%20EXZ`}
      />
    </div>

    <footer class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-gray-200">
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">
        <strong>About Ing Heng Credit:</strong> Over 40 years of experience financing heavy commercial vehicles, machinery, and equipment for Malaysian businesses. We understand your industry because we've been part of it for four decades.
      </p>
    </footer>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
